#grandmorning #family 🤗 Ready to #share what's always been kept close to my heart. ❤️ Creating that Deeply Nurture Human Heart When we quiet the mind, we can have ears that can hear. The still voice inside BOLDLY whispers…. “Create, Design, build, and grow with ALL that RICHLY nurtures THE human heart, mind, and body.” Shhh… can you hear it? What is it saying to you? --TL Brooks #hope #purpose #product #technology #grind #jounalism #writetoinspire #inspirewellbeing #wordshavepower #leadership #namaste 🕉️🦋🕯️

What an incredible #story that I am so thankful to witness. 💓 Perhaps the power of #storytelling + this story can continue to inform, redirect, and shape our society's fabric. 🦋 May the movie be poignant enough to shake us out of our slumber and hold ourselves, not the justice system, accountable to take #action and get #involved 🙏🏽 #loveheals 💖💖💖 Prayerfully for our children's sake. 🫶 #hope #protectourchildren #children #soundofhope #healing #story #change #possumtrot #adoption #angel 🕉️
